category: Games
requires: cygwin libfreetype6 libGL1 libpng15 libSDL1.2_0 libSDL_mixer1.2_0 libxml2 lua
sdesc: "2D Action/RPG space game"
ldesc: "Naev is a 2D space trading and combat game, in a similar vein to
Escape Velocity.

Naev is played from a top-down perspective, featuring fast-paced combat, many
ships, a large variety of equipment and a large galaxy to explore. The game is
highly open-ended, letting you proceed at your own pace."
